                     <interp inst="t17740413-93-off469" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17740413-93-off469" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a silver watch, value 40 s. a half guinea and four and sixpence in money, numbered, the property of 
                     <persName id="t17740413-93-person816">
                        Richard
                         Ryan
                     <interp inst="t17740413-93-person816" type="surname" value="Ryan"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17740413-93-person816" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
